:0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T21:32:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2/3</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講埋點解"},{"pid":"4a89727a9a2e50596c7d151f686897a76d31d79d","tid":382581,"uid":37297,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T21:34:53.000Z","msg":"假設3張牌嘅兩面分別係: <br />\n黑黑: A B<br />\n白白: C D<br />\n黑白: E(黑) F(白)<br />\n<br />\n抽出黎果面係黑色, 即係A, B, E其中一面<br />\n如果係A或者B反轉都係黑色, 所以係2/3"},{"pid":"38a10b2a3be7093995fa21556edd8865536b2c7c","tid":382581,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T21:47:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>究竟要有咁嘅數學推理要點先做到，太強了</blockquote><br />\n未有人答岩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果你係想人計埋第一面黑色嘅機會<br />\n咁你條題問錯<br />\n因為你話係已經知一邊係黑色</blockquote><br />\n冇人叫你計第一面係黑色既機會</blockquote><br />\nBTW 你講下你點計先"},{"pid":"acd140e9521c3ab9ebed6f37312dc14f6a0757dd","tid":382581,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T21:47:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>P(b assuming a)?</blockquote><br />\nyes"},{"pid":"ec3fcf8eedd540fe17662655176960b44f664c2e","tid":382581,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T22:34:53.000Z","msg":"邊個偷偷地負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6516850b82939636c67836d8241f047008776d","tid":382581,"uid":38017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T22:52:25.000Z","msg":"中學雞冇做功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e061809f2aa0a3d9cde2b9d42a83460088f2df5","tid":382581,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T23:11:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中學雞冇做功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n介唔介意幫手做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f550b25c4032426964e2e70564a2bece2b8275c","tid":382581,"uid":41887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:40:47.000Z","msg":"反正樓主都世界大戰開<br />\n下次不如開個0.999... = 1 既post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fdf106b1b5ad522a6d81d255ebbdc8c8632975a","tid":382581,"uid":136640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:51:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>袋入面有三張牌，一張兩面都係黑色，一張兩面都係白色，一張一面黑色一面白色。 <br />\n<br />\n而家你抽左一張出黎，見到佢面向你果面係黑色，咁請問佢另一面都係黑色既機率係幾多？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n命名先：<br />\nA係兩黑<br />\nB係一黑一白<br />\nC係兩白<br />\n<br />\n前設面係黑色既 C果張唔洗理 得番AB<br />\n<br />\n再將AB分成上下面<br />\nA上黑 A下黑 B上黑 B下白<br />\n<br />\n首先抽到面係黑色得三種case <br />\n             A上黑 A下黑 B上黑<br />\n（反面 A下黑 A上黑 B下白）<br />\n<br />\n反面係黑色就係2/3<br />\n<br />\n如果計埋前設面可以黑 可以白<br />\n6個面 3面黑 即係x多1/2<br />\nAns. 1/3<br />\n<br />\n(睇Liar game la凸你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"f8fd0d47b6d2e655d403f07235ed4feec190dac6","tid":382581,"uid":26084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T03:58:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>究竟要有咁嘅數學推理要點先做到，太強了</blockquote><br />\n未有人答岩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果你係想人計埋第一面黑色嘅機會<br />\n咁你條題問錯<br />\n因為你話係已經知一邊係黑色</blockquote><br />\n冇人叫你計第一面係黑色既機會</blockquote><br />\nBTW 你講下你點計先</blockquote><br />\n手上已經係黑色，後面一係黑一係白，所以 1/2"},{"pid":"0fdba752a30c8bb2475a8c72db6382d9a59ffedf","tid":382581,"uid":26084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T04:06:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>究竟要有咁嘅數學推理要點先做到，太強了</blockquote><br />\n未有人答岩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果你係想人計埋第一面黑色嘅機會<br />\n咁你條題問錯<br />\n因為你話係已經知一邊係黑色</blockquote><br />\n冇人叫你計第一面係黑色既機會</blockquote><br />\nBTW 你講下你點計先</blockquote><br />\n手上已經係黑色，後面一係黑一係白，所以 1/2</blockquote><br />\n因為面已開，唔會計算入去"},{"pid":"71d86a0b5edb25e24ec1bfa26c64b2b35b4a2b03","tid":382581,"uid":91502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T04:24:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1/2 秒<br />\n一邊黑<br />\n另一邊一係黑一係白 given你果三張</blockquote><br />\n屌 我計錯 好撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b98b2ccc4c1248b5cc4e5c5752dafc5bdd24ea","tid":382581,"uid":117944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T04:38:26.000Z","msg":"抽到兩面黑的機會係1/3<br />\n抽到黑色面向上的機會係3/6=1/2<br />\n咁你個condition係黑色面向上，然後另一面係黑色的機會率，就會係<br />\n(1/3)/(1/2)=2/3"},{"pid":"f3e5ab58fecf553902259607c6eb9257b07990e0","tid":382581,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T04:47:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反正樓主都世界大戰開<br />\n下次不如開個0.999... = 1 既post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n太低質。"},{"pid":"4bb9cdc3c2958f37e4b8e438794e8df80d5a8aaf","tid":382581,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T04:52:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1/2 秒<br />\n一邊黑<br />\n另一邊一係黑一係白 given你果三張</blockquote><br />\n屌 我計錯 好撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你應該係第一個認自己計錯數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b978fb087f156eb3f9415c7d4f886d6b2f8e3e","tid":382581,"uid":41432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T05:34:08.000Z","msg":"我覺保持1/3<img src=\"/assets/faces/no