ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T13:23:30.000Z","msg":"我係今年dse既,但我可以同大家講我讀左咁耐數冇做過一條問題要用到P(A|B)=xxx/xxx呢條公式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問親所謂已知都只係要響分子分母減番若干個case<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a570f675d0316f363c0ebe4aaf243215be19b1d","tid":382581,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T13:26:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係今年dse既,但我可以同大家講我讀左咁耐數冇做過一條問題要用到P(A|B)=xxx/xxx呢條公式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問親所謂已知都只係要響分子分母減番若干個case<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ndse level如果你明白個concept的確唔駛用條式去限死自己<br />\n但如果你讀到ug level bayesian theorem就會好重要, 因為到時就係deal with general results多過咁樣計條數"},{"pid":"38177d85b272870b5b1624e4caf522a874d26bdd","tid":382581,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T13:32:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主dse定中3?<br />\n無心冒犯</blockquote><br />\n小學"},{"pid":"a815209a0c1680514bea788fb859d80319477b66","tid":382581,"uid":108247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:27:42.000Z","msg":"有啲似一條好出名既數學題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有3度門個個"},{"pid":"4712f3f42d0b6740c3d8b748e8aac29d40ef5686","tid":382581,"uid":112340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:53:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://youtu.be/ky4HRe-vmxE?t=16m15s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fky4HRe-vmxE%3Ft%3D16m15s&d=nm5ttnAjW2eYY0XihQiG%2F%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=e14b18e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/ky4HRe-vmxE?t=16m15s</a><br />\n<br />\nLiar game<br />\n唔exactly 同一個情景 但類似"},{"pid":"5e1944235f856d607f5cd46306b9140c329caf22","tid":382581,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:18:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果係已知一邊係黑色，我認為個答案係2/3無問題<br />\n但佢係假設望到黑色，就唔係咁計了</blockquote><br />\n已知其中一邊係黑色先係1/2  望到一邊係2/3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗真d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想睇你用計出黎，應該我地是但一邊有邏輯上既錯誤</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔用貝氏公式，純粹數case計。<br />\n<br />\n所有case：<br />\n<br />\n1. 抽中黑黑卡，面向黑色面 = 1/3*1<br />\n2. 抽中白白卡，面向白色面 = 1/3*1<br />\n3. 抽中黑白卡，面向黑色面 = 1/3*1/2<br />\n4. 抽中黑白卡，面向白色面 = 1/3*1/2<br />\n<br />\nA. Given 抽完卡，唔望，第三者話你知其中一面係黑色<br />\n合條件既case有 1, 3, 4 <br />\n<br />\n所以黑黑機會= case1 / (case1+case3+case4)<br />\n=(1/3) / (1/3+1/3*1/2+1/3*1/2)<br />\n=(1/3) / (2/3)<br />\n=1/2<br />\n<br />\nB. Given 抽完卡，面向黑色面<br />\n合條件既case有 1,3<br />\n<br />\n所以黑黑機會=case1 / (case1+case3)<br />\n=(1/3) / (1/3+1/3*1/2)<br />\n=(1/3) / (1/2)<br />\n=2/3"},{"pid":"be17bb52aa0561f87ab99841178837710a191058","tid":382581,"uid":14867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T19:33:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>2/3 既意義在於 <br />\n<br />\n你重覆抽卡抽600次，入面大概會有300次你會見到黑色面先，而呢300次入面大概有200次係全黑果張。<br />\n<br />\n唔信可以試下人手又好excel又好做下實驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但你set咗已知係抽到黑色<br />\n<br />\nA:黑黑<br />\nB:白白<br />\nC:黑白<br />\n<br />\n你已知係抽到A黑黑，c黑白<br />\n<br />\n所以只會有a/c<br />\n<br />\n所以應該係1/2</blockquote><br />\n黑黑有兩面黑喎要計兩次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實條問題關鍵係你點樣execute<br />\n如果你係抽張卡，再random望其中一面的話2/3就成立。<br />\n如果係抽完之後只望正/反面，咁1/2就合理啲</blockquote><br />\n你調轉左。<br />\n而且1/2 係要你抽左出黎，唔望，某人話俾你知其中一面係黑色，咁先成立</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗你倒轉咗，refer to 你最尾個comment 只有1,3先成立，因為係你<span style=\"color: red;\">自己隨機揀一面嚟望</span>，所以係<br />\n(1/3) / (1/3*1/2+1/3)=2/3"},{"pid":"22a68df2385dbcc6c16ecabfa67cc0eca8d6a261","tid":382581,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T19:47:17.000Z","msg